description: Krupanalini & Majojkumar are a super cool couple that combined their authentic culinary customs, acquired a mobile kitchen, curated the freshest ingredients, and are now cruising their big beautiful truck through Boston. Stop by for a bite and try the best Biryani, along with other Indian fare favorites, like Chicken Tikka Masala, Lamb, Palak Paneer, and more!For your next flavorful fix, this is the truck to choose because you don’t want to miss a chance to indulge in tasty Indian bliss.
name: Indulge India
